 #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMKy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=be1e669f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"834e5e5f174be50fc0a21bf79ab98d1a5c4d87d5","tid":1552654,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4271f7ef0921b9d1fa95d2b4f885d1efca3581f6","tid":1552654,"uid":44831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"係，即係點，千字文<br />\n不過點解老豆搵日咁多前線狗唔斬斬件槍房"},{"pid":"b4c850d7625e8e09ba824c2e89fbcd2a68bcd628","tid":1552654,"uid":62514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4271f7ef0921b9d1fa95d2b4f885d1efca3581f6","tid":1552654,"uid":44831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"狗有account上黎扮示威者"},{"pid":"471c3653c53c9929f1d5d8363d8d561e3688c2c7","tid":1552654,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"跳樓墮海無可疑"},{"pid":"25f20821d81c705e24b9d35be726c4aea8433a4d","tid":1552654,"uid":280847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"如果關反修例事，一早就攪大件事啦"},{"pid":"5f9edb28813c2024e23876bb2aa5df23e01899c8","tid":1552654,"uid":291750,"like":1,